latestIgtvVideos.title: Do #korean beauty hacks work on indian skin?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Koreans have  been known for their flawless skin products and lately they have become very famous for  various beauty hacks which are trending all over the internet, this made me wonder whether these beauty hacks would actually work on Indian skin.
Something that has recently caught my eye is this automated facial cleanser, it supposed to increase blood circulation and remove makeup and dead cells and over all improve complection if used as a daily skin routine.
So after watching several beauty tutorials from various beauty bloggers across the world and reading a ton of reviews,I found out that there are several available in the market varying from a few thousand rupees to a few hundred rupees.
Since this was just an experiment I decided to go with  the cheapest and best option, I got mine form Amazon which was selling on half the price of nykaa..
So heres my review in this product..
I recommend using it on alternate days to start with before trying it everyday...
enjoy...

latestIgtvVideos.title: Guide to a #fun afternoon @timesquarerestobar
Absolutely loved the food at @svasaofficial al
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
join me on a virtual journey at our experience dining at @svasaofficial @svahofficial curated by Chef Deena @chef_dinakar .
We has the pleasure of trying the chef tasting menu that is available for dinner.
This is a 7 course pure vegetarian meal curated to tease and inspire the pallet, the favours so authentic to the tamil cuisine yet presented to push the imagination and tastebuds.. each element so perfectly prepared and adding so much value to the plate!
Paying homage to native ingredients and 2000 to 3000 year recipies that they have personally done so much research on and developed into mouth watering satiating dishes that pictures and words just don't do justice in capturing.
The meal was thought provoking and naustalgic at the same time with familiar flavors presented like you would never predict.
The best part was since it was a sreerams birthday @rogue_program and a special occasion for the family.. a make shift cake made of buttermilk foam and a hidden suprise, designed to turn the humble curdrice which happens to be a favourite dish was the  cherry on the cake!
Each course was generous in portion, tasted fantastic and it was exciting to eat.

⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ and a must try!
from my end...

latestIgtvVideos.title: #staycation at @thebluehouseecr
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The blue house is a large beautiful property located just after the Sholinganallur junction before the toll booth on ECR High road.
 This place is it true treasure due to the sheer size as well as the luxurious 5 bedroom villa situated at the centre of it. 
The grounds also accommodates huge swimming pool area with attached bath, changing rooms and even a viewpoint overlooking the beautiful beach which can even be hired separately for a day.
 This location is a perfect getaway and one of the best locations I could find to host small parties for friends and family, with its large halls and living areas it makes it ideal for the group to enjoy time together along with enjoying the views of beautiful gardens and ofcourse the sea.

The property even has its own private entrance to the beach , what more does one need!

Join me as I take you on a virtual journey of this Gorgeous property.

Get in touch with @thebluehouseecr
for enquiries.

latestIgtvVideos.title: The @meadowlaneecr #staycation
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
If you need a quick getaway which is not too far from the city,@meadowlaneecr is located in akkarai, a quaint 2 bhk with a large garden area and outdoor fountain dineing table, outdoor shower area and pool, a private cottage villa with 24 hours security , wifi and access to the beach is all ul ever need. 
This was the perfect pick for my family, and had something for everyone of all ages .. from my elderly in-laws @lathuskitchen to my teenage cousin's @adhreshya @shrdhavijay.. even for some romance with @rogue_program...
with out the scare of being exposed to covid..as the place is cleaned and sanitized before you check in!
 
It even comes with a small equipped kitchen to wip up quick meals and is located not far away from the many eatery and restaurant options ecr has to offer..
With a care taker at ur Beck n call this place is the perfect mix of luxury and privacy...

latestIgtvVideos.title: #throwbackthursday ...The @louvreabudhabi ..
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
it's been a long time since I posted a travel blog unfortunately due to the times travelling is become quite a task, so I thought why not a trip down memory lane.
The is a video for all the #artlovers out there.. this is a must visit place.. 
These clips are from a visit I did in 2019.. and I was mind-blown at the mammoth collection of art and antiquities.
Having been able to witness so many famous paintings n sculptures from different Times in history made me feel more rooted and humbled.. the structure itself is so different and intimidating that you feel like you are inside an alien spacecraft giving you an unearthly unique experience.
